episodes.title: Giambattista Valli SS16 Backstage x Gigi Hadid| Paris Fashion Week

She talks to us the impact of the bold viral post that she recently shared with her 7.2 million Instagram followers. Hadid had received numerous negative comments on the popular social media app, with some criticizing her curves, slightly jumpy walk and reality show pedigree. On September 28th she defended herself and with a passionate, heartfelt post on her Instagram feed: “No, I don’t have the same body type as the other models in shows…I’m a hard worker that’s confident in myself, one that came at a time where the fashion industry was ready for a change.” We caught up with Gigi backstage at Spring 2016 Paris Fashion Week to find out more about her empowering message for women everywhere.  Reported, Executive Produced and Directed by Karen Morrison.

Backstage as makeup artist Pat McGrath gave the models bold red lips, hairstylist Guido explained that their side swept hairdos were meant to make them look like a "naughty, innocent troubled girl".

episodes.title: Alexander McQueen's Final Paris Show Plato's Atlantis Spring 2010
episodes.author: modtv@mac.com (Karen Morrison | MOD-TV.COM)
episodes.summary: Go backstage at Alexander McQueen's final show in Paris for Spring 2010 called Plato's Atlantis. The 40 year old award-winning British designer was a visionary who liked to blow people's minds staging the most epic, cinematic fashion shows in the world. Alexander McQueen died tragically on Thursday, February 11, 2010. The world of fashion will never be the same without him.

episodes.title: Louis Vuitton Spring 2010 Backstage | Paris Fashion Week
episodes.author: modtv@mac.com (Karen Morrison | MOD-TV.COM)
episodes.summary: Louis Vuitton Designer Marc Jacobs creates a collection that is fun, young and for new age travelers. As Marc explained after the show "style is about your own expression". Find out why Katy Perry loves his sense of style. Makeup by Pat McGrath and Hair by Guido.

The fantasy show, staged at the Grand Palais was a jaw dropping visual experience featuring a recreation of the Champs-Elysees, the Eiffel Tower and models dancing and swinging on gigantic floats.

episodes.author: modtv@mac.com (Karen Morrison | MOD-TV.COM)

This 22 year old beauty from Melbourne Australia ruled the catwalk in Milan and Paris this season, booked at every top show from Versace to Lanvin. Here's our exclusive look backstage with Abbey Lee as she reflects on her successful Spring 2010 season.

episodes.author: modtv@mac.com (Karen Morrison | MOD-TV.COM)
episodes.summary: Marc Jacobs Spring show is the hot ticket of NY Fashion week. His Spring 2010 collection was romantic and dark, inspired by the theatre and ballet the show was simply spectacular. Featuring Francois Nars, Rachel Zoe, Hilary Alexander and Bryan Boy.

episodes.title: Michael Angel Spring 2010 Backstage | New York Fashion Week
episodes.author: modtv@mac.com (Karen Morrison | MOD-TV.COM)
episodes.summary: Australian born New York designer Michael Angel has hit is stride with his new Spring 2010 collection that is sexy, playful and full of color. Top Model Julia Stegner takes us backstage and makeup artist Charlotte Willer of Maybelline New York gives us the inside scoop on the sun kissed look she created for this stunning show.

episodes.title: Pat McGrath Backstage: Meet the World's Most Influential Makeup Artist

episodes.summary: Pat McGrath is the most influential makeup artist in the world, and in one season does over 27 major shows from Dior to Gucci. Here's our exclusive look at Pat in action backstage and find out why all the top models and designers love her. Featuring Lily Donaldson, Chanel Iman, Raquel Zimmerman Stella McCartney, Marc Jacobs, John Galliano, Alber Elbaz and Oliver Theyskens.

episodes.title: Burberry Prosum Fall 2009 Backstage Christopher Bailey | Milan Fashion Week
episodes.author: modtv@mac.com (Karen Morrison | MOD-TV.COM)
episodes.summary: British Designer Christopher Bailey's winning forumla for Burberry is creating collections that are rooted in reality but are always cool. For Fall 2009 is a contradiction between strong and soft, keeping the focus on the trenchcoat. "This is a moment for thoughtful fashion" Bailey explains. Featuring Lily Donaldson, Mario Testino and makeup artist Wendy Rowe.

episodes.title: Stella McCartney Fall 2009 Backstage | Paris Fashion Week
episodes.author: modtv@mac.com (Karen Morrison | MOD-TV.COM)

episodes.author: modtv@mac.com (Karen Morrison | MOD-TV.COM)
episodes.summary: Designer Alber Elbaz creates another stunning collection for Lanvin. His Fall 2009 collection is dramatic, rich and very chic. Go backstage with Pat McGrath, Guido Palau and top model Natasha Poly

episodes.title: Louis Vuitton Fall 2009 Backstage | Paris Fashion Week
episodes.author: modtv@mac.com (Karen Morrison | MOD-TV.COM)
episodes.summary: "Life's a blast, you might as well enjoy it" Marc Jacobs told us backstage at his Louis Vuitton Fall 2009 Collection in Paris. This has to be the sexiest, most upbeat show of the Fall season.The look is a sexy Playboy bunny with a touch of Brigitte Bordot. Love it!

episodes.title: Michael Kors Fall 2009 Backstage | New York Fashion Week
episodes.author: modtv@mac.com (Karen Morrison | MOD-TV.COM)
episodes.summary: According to New York designer Michael Kors it's the balance between fantasy and reality that makes fashion work. His Fall 2009 collection strikes that balance perfectly. It's powerful, confident and chic and very urban which means it's full of black clothes every woman can wear. But it's the acid bright neon colors that makes this collection a real winner.

episodes.title: Diane Von Furstenberg Fall 2009 Backstage | New York Fashion Week
episodes.author: modtv@mac.com (Karen Morrison | MOD-TV.COM)
episodes.summary: Diane Von Furstenberg's collection for Fall 2009 was designed for global normads - women who love to travel, like to layer up and create their own individual look. As Ms. Furstenberg explains "clothes should be your friends" and your closet should be full of the pieces you love. Featuring top models Chanel Iman and Behati Prinsloo. Makeup by James Kaliardos.

episodes.title: Supermodel Gemma Ward Backstage
episodes.author: modtv@mac.com (Karen Morrison | MOD-TV.COM)
episodes.summary: Gemma Ward is only 18 and is fashion's current "it" girl. Born on November 3, 1987 in Perth Austrialia she was discovered in 2002 at an Australian TV Show "Search for a Supermodel" which she was persuaded to enter. In three years Gemma has been on campaigns from Prada to Burberry, and every major fashion designer from Louis Vuitton to Dior book her to do their fashion shows. We caught up with Gemma backstage in NY, Milan and Paris to see what the dreamy life as a top model is really like.

episodes.author: modtv@mac.com (Karen Morrison | MOD-TV.COM)
episodes.summary: Every season there are are bevy of new models who hit the runway who have the dream of becoming a star. This season we couldn’t help but notice Elite Model Emina Cunmalaj. What’s it like being a new girl on the scene who wants to make it? MODTV went to Paris to find out.
